headline: Sports Analytics Market worth $4.75 billion by 2030 | MarketsandMarkets™
summary: According to MarketsandMarkets™, the global Sports Analytics Market size is projected to reach USD 4.75 billion by 2030 from USD 2.29 billion in 2025, at a CAGR of 15.7% during the forecast period.
